data.description: Beautifully updated 3 bedroom townhome in sought after Garden Lakes community. Wood look tile throughout with carpet on stairs. One bedroom is on the first floor and 2 bedrooms on the second floor. Inviting Primary suite with updated dual vanity and an abundance of closet space. Gas fireplace in Living room. Private, fenced and partially screened patio is perfect for entertaining or relaxing. Shed for extra storage. Short walk to community rec center. Pet friendly and low HOA fees. Walk to grocery store, great restaurants & shopping. Close to 95, Turnpike, airport and beaches! Great P. B. Gardens schools. Garden Lakes is a beautiful DiVosta community located on 87+ acres of winding lakes and green space. Come see why Palm Beach Gardens was voted a ''Top City to Live in Florida'' in 2019!
